long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The opCyberMartians are a group of adventurous Martians residing in an untapped Martian world. This world is abundant with various mineral resources, awaiting exploration and utilization for the establishment of a brand-new Martian Cyber city. You can mine minerals, trade them, and use them to construct buildings and vehicles. By selling mineral-laden vehicles, you can earn Token.
